I"ƒ<p>A delivery crowdsourcing application that enables an easy and hassle-free intra-campus delivery system. (Currently only for food)</p>

<p><strong>Aim -</strong></p>

<p>To develop a human-centered application that is easy and convinient to use.</p>

<p><strong>Features -</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Get food delivered to your location and pay the cost for food only. To pay delivery charges, use the in-app virtual currency <strong>‚Äúsuper coins‚Äù</strong>.</li>
  <li>Earn the virtual currency by delivering food to those in-need.</li>
  <li>Easy to order from the menu provided by canteen and in-campus cafe.</li>
  <li>Easy to deliver and earn super coins from a dedicated marketplace which shows all live orders.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Process -</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>After rigorous ideation and contextual inquiries, we created an affinity diagram on the basis of responses by students.</li>
</ul>

<p><img class="long-img" src="/assets/img/pc-affinity-low.jpg" /></p>

<p>After the affinity diagram, we designed a low-fidelity prototype and did task analysis with students. Then as per iterative process, we refined the design and finally developed the android application.</p>

